y of salvation for Muslims. His work contributes to contemporary dilemmas and challenges on the nature of religion.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aEast and WestxHistoryy17th century. 0aIslamxStudy and teachingzEuropexHistory. 0aMiddle East specialistszEuropevBiography. 7aRELIGION / Islam / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertGorgias Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076710040uhttps://doi.org/10.31826/978146324440840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781463244408423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781463244408/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  a978-3-11-076710-0  Gorgias Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK